response.overview: In the Netherlands, the ocean is rising. A reclusive engineer has arrived in Rotterdam, promising to invent a new system of dikes and dams, using a computer that harnesses the power of dreams. A pair of twins are selected for the study - gabber kids, from the local hardcore scene. As the duo get sucked deeper into a digital dream world, they begin to wonder if the inventor's true goal isn't to protect Rotterdam at all.
response.title: Culturesport: Rotterdam 1995
